## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b7eac-208">下列範例會將這個屬性設定為在對 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.ProxyAddress%2A> 屬性所指定之 Proxy 傳送要求時使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b7eac-208">The following example sets this property to use when sending requests to the proxy specified in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.ProxyAddress%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
